org.daisy.common.xproc

Class XProcPipelineInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.daisy.common.xproc.XProcPipelineInfo

  • public final class XProcPipelineInfo
extends Object
    The Class XProcPipelineInfo gives access to the collection of ports and options from a pipeline. This class is immutable, in order to give actual values to ports and options use an XProcInput object.

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      static class  XProcPipelineInfo.Builder
      The XProcPipelineInfo Builder allows to build the pipline info, this class is for internal use of the xproc implementation bundle.
